replies.body:
he has stupid high damage late game with his q spam, great aoe damage and kiting potential. if you take tp you can make enemy baron dragon attempts risky for the enemy team (i got a quad once by tping to baron while the enemy was taking) he also isn't blue reliant and can do 1K damage with ult alone late game with about 800 ap. You also don't have to worry as much about getting dived because of your passive.

downside

- q hard to land/easy to dodge 

- mana hungry early (cannot use E or w early or you will run oom)

- squishy until rod of ages

- ult is easily countered by spellshields/ zhonya's/ Magic resist

